					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "The Orechid"
			x: 7.0d
			y: -6.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["4CCA4B2A9DAE30AE"]
			description: ["A manually-fed Crushing Wheel setup is a permanent bottleneck. An Andesite Funnel mounted on a Chest pulls items onto a Mechanical Belt, which carries them to a Chute that drops ore directly into the input gap above your wheels. On the output side, add a Brass Funnel with a filter to sort crushed ore from byproducts into separate inventories. Once this line runs unattended, your metal throughput becomes limited only by your belt speed and available power."]
			id: "1C4D7E9F2A3B5C69"
			rewards: [{
				count: 4
				id: "4C6E8A2B1D3F5A85"
