		}
		{
			dependencies: ["378C3A0358FD2ABD"]
			description: ["The Water Wheel is your first reliable power source. Place it where flowing water runs perpendicular to the wheel's axle. Two Water Wheels on the same shaft double your output. Look for rivers and waterfalls early — optimal placement is worth more than additional wheels."]
