		}
		{
			dependencies: ["369A9E51C5A05AB7"]
			description: ["Cogwheels transfer rotation between adjacent shafts. Meshing a Large Cogwheel with a standard one creates a speed ratio — use this to tune machine RPM without adding more power sources. Every machine has an optimal speed range; running too slow wastes time, running too fast burns SU."]
