		{
			dependencies: ["378C3A0358FD2ABD"]
			description: ["Immersive Engineering's Alloy Bricks are needed to build the Alloy Kiln, which produces Brass Ingots by mixing Copper and Zinc. A modest material cost now unlocks Create's entire Brass tier of machinery — the most impactful upgrade in early Create progression."]
