		{
			dependencies: ["39C72E59C80B3EB3"]
			description: ["Brass Ingots are alloyed from Copper and Zinc in a heated Mixer. They unlock the entire Brass age of Create machinery, including the Sequenced Gearshift, Mechanical Arm, and Deployer. You cannot progress past early Create without a reliable brass supply."]
