		{
			dependencies: [
				"05504D33EF04161E"
				"4F9FCFD4864B0663"
			]
			description: ["The Precision Mechanism is an intricate assembly of gears, springs, and tubing assembled in a Mechanical Crafter. It is the gateway component to the Mechanical Arm and other advanced Brass machines. Building a Mechanical Crafter to produce it is itself a small automation challenge worth solving properly."]
