			description: ["Large Cogwheels mesh with standard Cogwheels to produce a 4:1 speed ratio. Place a Large Cogwheel adjacent to a standard one with perpendicular shafts to multiply or divide RPM. Use them to push fast-throughput machines like Crushing Wheels or Saws to their maximum speed."]
