		{
			dependencies: ["7D2E4F6A8B1C3D56"]
			description: ["GregTech Community Edition is the industrial backbone of the late game. It begins simply — hand tools, iron, and fire — and escalates into vast automated factories processing every ore and alloy on the periodic table. Reaching Spirit Scholar means your cultivation has stabilized enough to direct that same discipline toward industry. The path from campfire smelting to electric machinery is long, but every step is deliberate."]
			id: "1727551BEC3E69D1"
