			dependencies: ["2B8D4F6A9E1C3B7D"]
			description: ["The Primitive Blast Furnace is constructed from 32 Firebricks arranged in a hollow 3x3x4 structure with the controller facing outward. Feed it Wrought Iron Ingots and Charcoal — the ratio is 1:2, iron to charcoal. The first batch of Steel marks the beginning of every machine chain that follows. Steel unlocks hulls, plates, pipes, and the frameworks for every GT multiblock you will ever build."]
