			x: 24.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["4E5D0AA37DD7A872"]
			description: ["GT Glass is produced by processing Flint into Flint Dust, sieving or macerating Sand into Quartz Sand Dust, mixing them to form Glass Dust, then smelting. Vacuum Tubes are the foundational electronic component of LV circuits — a Glass Tube, two Copper Foil pieces, and a Steel Rod soldered together on a circuit board. Craft two: they are required for the Basic Electronic Circuit."]
			id: "4E2F7A9D1B5C8E6A"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
