			title: "Red Alloy & Circuit Board"
			x: 28.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["54851FB08D5C6931"]
			description: ["The LV Machine Hull is the chassis for every LV electric machine. It requires Steel Plates, Wrought Iron Plates, and Tin Single Cables — the Tin cable demands rubber coating, which is why Rubber gates this quest. Nine steel plates form the outer shell; the wrought iron and tin cable provide internal structure and a low-voltage bus bar. Every LV machine in this chapter starts here."]
			id: "3A9E7B2D4F8C6A1E"
			rewards: [{
				count: 3
