			x: 32.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["6B4C8F3E1A9D5B7F"]
			description: ["Soul Sand, drawn from the Nether, carries latent spiritual resonance — the same force cultivators spend lifetimes purifying. Alloyed with Invar under heat, it yields the Soul Infused Ingot. Draw this into wire and it becomes a conductor that carries both electricity and soul energy simultaneously. LV Energy Converters require it specifically: without soul resonance threaded through the circuitry, the conversion between GT and standard power formats is unstable. The industrial and the spiritual are not separate systems."]
			id: "1C7D5F9A4B2E8C3A"
			rewards: [{
				count: 3
