		}
		{
			dependencies: ["6B4C8F3E1A9D5B7F"]
			description: ["The LV Electric Motor converts electrical current into mechanical rotation. It is a direct prerequisite for most LV machines — the Macerator, Wiremill, Bender, Lathe, and Assembler all require one. Craft it from Iron Rod, Copper Single Wire, and a Tin Cable wound in the correct configuration using GT hand tools. The motor is cheap; building multiples now saves time when the rest of the LV machine suite comes online."]
			id: "4D1E3B7C8F6A2D9B"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "691F5BBBF1BC886C"
