				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "LV Chemical Bath"
			x: 48.0d
			y: 3.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["20078A3EE4C9425E"]
			description: ["The complete electric ore processing chain is assembled. A single raw ore input now produces two to four distinct output items — base ore dust, a secondary byproduct dust, a tertiary chemical byproduct, and Stone Dust from the washing step. Run everything through all four stages before final smelting. The average effective yield across common ores reaches 3.2x per raw ore input. Create's Crushing Wheels were a step. This is the destination."]
			id: "7A9F036C8676F320"
			rewards: [{
				count: 5
				id: "12340000AABB000E"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_gold"
