				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Blood Altar"
			x: 48.0d
			y: -6.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2354575E7D73E76D"]
			description: ["The Water Sigil creates infinite water sources by spending Life Essence — right-click any air block above a valid surface and it places a permanent water source block. This feeds GT Steam Boilers, Ore Washers, and any water-hungry machine indefinitely without pumps, aqueducts, or player intervention. GT's industrial output enables Blood Magic's construction. Blood Magic's magic supplies GT's most tedious resource. Neither system is complete without the other."]
			id: "41E155533627CFD4"
			optional: true
			rewards: [{
				count: 3
