			title: "Water Sigil"
			x: 50.0d
			y: -6.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: [
				"43CBA3E6F9CF363F"
				"5A5B0002CCDD0002"
			]
			description: ["Cupronickel is alloyed from Copper and Nickel in a 1:1 ratio in the Alloy Smelter. Draw the ingots through the Wiremill to produce Cupronickel Double Wire, then assemble four wire units into Cupronickel Coil Blocks — the heating element of the Electric Blast Furnace. In this pack, the Cupronickel Coil Block recipe requires Naga Scales from the Twilight Forest Naga; open the Medium Voltage chapter and begin the Naga hunt before attempting to craft coil blocks. At 1800K maximum temperature, Cupronickel coils smelt Aluminum, Silicon, and Magnesium: the materials that unlock the MV Machine Hull and the entire MV tier. Every LV machine you have built was preparation for this coil."]
			id: "2AEDD3EF2A946CA6"
			rewards: [{
				count: 5
				id: "12340000AABB0014"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_gold"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "gear"
			size: 1.5d
			tasks: [
				{
