			title: "Into the Volt Age"
			x: 56.0d
			y: -2.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["43CBA3E6F9CF363F"]
			description: ["The Twilight Forest is entered by constructing a 2×2 pool of water, surrounding it with flowers on all sides, and dropping a Diamond into the center. The portal ignites when the conditions are met. The realm beyond is a permanent overcast dimension — no natural sky light, dense tree cover, and escalating boss guardians that enforce a strict progression order. The Naga is the first guardian. Its Scales are required in this pack to craft Cupronickel Coil Blocks; without them, the Electric Blast Furnace cannot be assembled. Enter the forest and begin the hunt before you attempt to finish your coil winding."]
			id: "5A5B0001CCDD0001"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "7A7B0001CCDD0001"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_gold"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [{
				dimension: "twilightforest:twilight_forest"
				id: "6A6B0001CCDD0001"
				type: "dimension"
			}]
			title: "The Twilight Forest"
			x: 52.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5A5B0001CCDD0001"]
			description: ["The Naga is a massive serpent that circles its clearing in aggressive territorial sweeps. Its primary attack is a rapid lateral lunge — clear the clearing of obstacles before engaging. When killed, it drops Naga Scales and the Naga Head. The Scales are woven into the Cupronickel Coil Block recipe in this pack; collect four then return to your factory to finish winding your EBF coils. The Naga is the first Twilight Forest gate; every subsequent boss requires you to have cleared all prior guardians."]
			id: "5A5B0002CCDD0002"
			rewards: [
				{
					count: 5
