				item: "twilightforest:naga_scale"
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "The Naga"
			x: 54.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2AEDD3EF2A946CA6"]
			description: ["The Electric Blast Furnace requires a shell of Steel Machine Casings — Hammered Steel Plates bent and assembled into structural heat-resistant frames. You need 32 for the outer wall of the 3×3×4 structure. The interior ring of Cupronickel Coil Blocks sits inside these casings and is replaced independently when upgrading to higher-temperature coils. Build the casing stockpile while you complete the Naga hunt — both must be ready simultaneously before the multiblock can be placed."]
			id: "5A5B0003CCDD0003"
			rewards: [{
				count: 3
				id: "7A7B0003CCDD0001"
