		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5A5B000ECCDD000E"]
			description: ["Kanthal Coil Blocks replace the Cupronickel inner ring of the EBF without dismantling the outer shell. Break only the inner coil layer, place Kanthal Coil Blocks in every inner-ring position, and the EBF controller automatically detects the upgrade. At 2700K the EBF reaches Titanium's smelting threshold (1941K) with 759K of thermal headroom — sufficient for every HV-tier alloy including Stainless Steel. Both production chains can begin as soon as the coil swap is complete."]
			id: "5A5B000FCCDD000F"
