		{
			dependencies: ["5A5B0010CCDD0010"]
			description: ["Stainless Steel is alloyed from Iron, Chrome, Nickel, and Manganese in the EBF. Chrome is produced by processing Chromite Ore through the Macerator to obtain Chromite Dust, then through the MV Electrolyzer to yield Chrome Ingots — the same pipeline introduced in the Kanthal Alloy chain. Nickel comes from Pentlandite ore; Manganese from Pyrolusite or as a processing byproduct. Your Kanthal Coils reach 2700K, comfortably above the Stainless Steel alloying range. Smelt at least 16 ingots — Stainless Steel is consumed by both the HV Hull and the Soul Forged Ingot recipe."]
