		{
			dependencies: ["7DB2759F155D5B2E"]
			description: ["The Advanced Electronic Circuit is the HV circuit tier. It requires Central Processing Units (CPUs) built from layered Silicon Wafers and Integrated Circuit Boards, assembled in the Assembler at HV speed. The production chain is longer than the Good Electronic Circuit — plan a dedicated Assembler line for CPU production before attempting circuit assembly. Advanced Electronic Circuits are consumed by every HV machine and by the first AE2 components you will encounter at EV tier."]
