		{
			dependencies: ["430AF7D410417947"]
			description: ["Soul Forged is the first alloy that cannot be explained by metallurgy alone. Spirit Iron Ingots from the Soul Land progression, Stainless Steel from the Electric Blast Furnace, and a Qi Crystal from your cultivation path are combined in a shaped crafting recipe — the crystal acts as a resonance anchor that aligns the metal's grain structure to soul power frequency. The resulting ingot is lighter than Steel and resonates with spirit energy, making it the ideal substrate for Mine & Slash Tier 3 gear at the M&S profession table. Every high-tier Soul Land equipment recipe from this point forward draws on it."]
